==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whisperer
<hw>Whis"per*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>One who whispers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A tattler; one who tells secrets; a conveyer of
intelligence secretly; hence; a backbiter; one who slanders
secretly.</def> <rj><au>Prov. xvi. 28.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whispering</ent>⟦br⟧
